edu.ucla.sspace.vector

Class MaskedDoubleVectorView

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.ucla.sspace.vector.MaskedDoubleVectorView
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DoubleVector, Vector<Double>, Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    MaskedSparseDoubleVectorView

    public class MaskedDoubleVectorView
extends Object
implements DoubleVector
    A decorator that masked view of a Vector through the use of a mapping from new column indices to original column indices. The size of the new vector is based on the number of valid mappings.
    Author:
    Keith Stevens
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
